<section class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About me</h2>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        I really love doing sports. I have tried many: 🤸🏼, ⚽, 🏃🏼‍♂️, 🏋🏼‍♂️, 🏊🏻‍♂️, 🏇🏼... and doing them, especially with other people, is probably one of the things that makes me most fulfilled and happy.
      </p>
      <p>
        These days, I'm running a little bit, but I still go to the gym so I can easily smash my brother at arm wrestling.
      </p>
      <p>
        Other things that I love are escape rooms, chess and kittens.
      </p>
      <p>
        During my free time, I pretend to be a software engineer 🤡. The projects I enjoy most are the ones that demand intense logical thinking and heavily rely on complex algorithms or data structures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .content a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .content a:hover {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
